that helps in delivering high-quality software faster and more reliably through automation and collaboration.
 
Gate Management in DevOps:
‚Ä¢	Acts as a control checkpoint
‚Ä¢	Used to decide when to allow a process or deployment to move forward
‚Ä¢	Helps in improving quality by catching issues early and reducing technical debt
 
DevOps is a combination of 3 things:
Tools
Used for automation, integration, and tracking:
‚Ä¢	Ansible ‚Äì Configuration management
‚Ä¢	Jenkins ‚Äì CI/CD automation
‚Ä¢	Jira ‚Äì Project and issue tracking
 
